        "content": "<p>Um. Did it ever occur to anyone that </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    <span class=\"cp\">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;OperationOutcome</span> <span class=\"na\">xmlns=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;http://hl7.org/fhir&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;text&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;status</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;generated&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">xmlns=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"nt\">&lt;p&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"nt\">&lt;b&gt;</span>Operation Outcome for :Validate resource <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/b&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/p&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;p&gt;</span>All OK<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/p&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/text&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/OperationOutcome&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>is not a valid Resource....?<br>\n... <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"191316\">@Grahame Grieve</span>  ...?</p>",
        "id": 153916387,
        "sender_full_name": "Simone Heckmann",
        "timestamp": 1509099601
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If I call /OperationOutcome/$validate for that on the very same server that gave me that very same response, I get</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">&lt;OperationOutcome&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;issue&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;severity</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;error&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;code</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;structure&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;details&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;text</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;Profile http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/OperationOutcome, Element &amp;quot;OperationOutcome.issue&amp;quot; (OperationOutcome.issue): minimum required = 1, but only found 0&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/details&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;location</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;OperationOutcome&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;expression</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;OperationOutcome // line 1 col 5)&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/issue&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/OperationOutcome&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>which is expected, since <em>issue</em> has a cadinality of 1..*</p>",
        "id": 153916388,
        "sender_full_name": "Simone Heckmann",
        "timestamp": 1509099787
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you can have non-error issues</p>",
